             was indicted for <rs id="t18290611-104-off550" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290611-104-off550" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-104-off550" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously forging a certain bill of exchange for payment of Â£200, purporting to be drawn by Smith and Co. on Cropper and Thomas, of Liverpool, with intent to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290611-104-victim789" type="victimName">
                           Frederick 
                           Roope
                        <interp inst="t18290611-104-victim789" type="surname" value="Roope"></interp>
